.TH "tipc_buf_acquire" 9 "tipc_buf_acquire" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
tipc_buf_acquire \- creates a TIPC message buffer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct sk_buff *" tipc_buf_acquire
.BI "(u32 size "  ","
.BI "gfp_t gfp "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "size" 12
message size (including TIPC header)
.IP "gfp" 12
memory allocation flags
.SH "RETURN"
a new buffer with data pointers set to the specified size.
.SH "NOTE"
Headroom is reserved to allow prepending of a data link header.
There may also be unrequested tailroom present at the buffer's end.
